{"tid":276623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人貪免費旅遊　冒險帶貨闖關","createTime":"2017-06-09T03:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T04:27:32.000Z","uid":20738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ffa3a6dfd1273791ca04525b46bc0e17bc0ec234","tid":276623,"uid":20738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:11:26.000Z","msg":"免費旅遊本身就係一個局<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170508/20014551\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170508%2F20014551&d=Qt0MqXQlWJQZma1h94VKXaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=db171c33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170508%2F20014551&h=8ef40cc4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170508/20014551</a><br />\n<br />\n港人貪免費旅遊　冒險帶貨闖關 日警告：走私黃金隨時坐監 |<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】隨着近年日韓成為港人旅遊熱門首選，有走私黃金集團覷準機會，藉大搞「三日兩夜免費團」或「日本水貨團」，以包機票、酒店及賺取報酬，招徠大批學生、情侶報團，實質引誘團友走私金條，結果在入境日韓時遭扣押。《蘋果》發現去年日本海關截獲的294宗走私黃金案件中，竟有近一半來自香港，日本駐港總領事館警告，走私黃金屬嚴重罪行，旅客隨時被判監。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者：黃學潤　郭美華　張軍"},{"pid":"1e019b974331a8cf21442ae144cdf71e236f5494","tid":276623,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T04:06:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4c873a2735872e2f779b965cf869e1def17d430","tid":276623,"uid":34029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T04:07:49.000Z","msg":"屌鳩大陸西 原來最鍾意走水貨係香港人"},{"pid":"a93ec885295b337bb1f080de4f89afba865707fc","tid":276623,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T04:09:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"748dc45e2def887169a41c07a0aaaea224f75198","tid":276623,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T04:14:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台狗有句說話：免費的其實最貴</blockquote><br />\n估唔到台狗都講到人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fb0c2c589a3873ed508181a665968efffbba4e","tid":276